<p>While a different account added: 'You always look gorgeous! Stay safe and great dedication! You are an inspiration.'  </p>

<p>It comes after Kym celebrated her 44th birthday in lockdown in June alongside her soldier boyfriend Scott Ratcliff and her three children. </p>

<p>The Coronation Street actress shared a sweet photo of her birthday display that included balloons, cake and cards.</p>

<p>Celebrations: It comes after Kym celebrated her 44th birthday in lockdown in June alongside her soldier boyfriend Scott Ratcliff and her three children</p>

<p>Kym thanked her family for making 'everything feel normal' in a lengthy caption to accompany the pic. </p>

<p>The actress was surprised with giant letters of her initials that were placed either side of the fireplace in their living room.  </p>

<p>Kym has children David, 25, Emily, 23, and Polly, nine. The soap star has suffered heartbreak during lockdown after loosing her uncle George to coronavirus.</p>

<p>She continued: 'Thank you from the bottom of my heart my wonderful family, boyfriend and friends. I am emotional and feel so loved! I love you all' (pictured with children David, 25, Emily, 23, and Polly, nine) </p>
